:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"<div>Un pense-b&ecirc;te dans la page d''&eacute;dition</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:85:"WordPress Francophone : L’Hebdo WordPress n° 242 : BuddyPress – 2015 – Podcast";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/qeRz470Kfzg/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/qeRz470Kfzg/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2014-10-21T07:26:59+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"Benoît";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4319:"<div>\n<h3>BuddyPress 2.1.1</h3>\n<p>Une version mineure de BuddyPress est disponible. <a href="https://buddypress.org/2014/10/buddypress-2-1-1/">Mettez &agrave; jour vers 2.1.1</a> (en).</p>\n<h3>Le Podcast n&deg;6 de VFT</h3>\n<p>D&eacute;j&agrave; 6 ! La nouvelle mouture du podcast de VFT est en ligne ! <a href="http://veryfrenchtrip-wp.eu/podcast-wordpress-6-business-themes-plugins-premium/">D&eacute;vorez-le</a> !</p>\n<h3>Le futur de WordPress</h3>\n<p><a href="http://inside.envato.com/the-future-of-wordpress/">Un article de juin dernier qui entreprend de faire le tour de l&rsquo;avenir de WordPress</a>. Attention, c&rsquo;est long&hellip; mais c&rsquo;est bon ! (en)</p>\n<h3>2015 est de sortie</h3>\n<p><a href="https://make.wordpress.org/core/2014/10/14/twenty-fifteen-is-here/">Le prochain th&egrave;me par d&eacute;faut</a> est sur les rails ! (en) &hellip; Olivier <a href="http://www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr/blog/technique/twenty-fifteen-simple-et-elegant/">vous en parle</a>.</p>\n<h3>HTTPS avec WordPress</h3>\n<p><a href="http://wpformation.com/wordpress-http-https/">Fabrice pr&eacute;sente comment s&eacute;curiser votre WordPress</a> gr&acirc;ce &agrave; SSL et passer votre site en https.</p>\n<h3>V&eacute;rifier le nombre d&rsquo;articles d&rsquo;un auteur</h3>\n<p>Si un auteur a publi&eacute; un article ou plus <a href="http://wpchannel.com/condition-verifier-auteur-publie-article-wordpress/">vous pouvez le savoir facilement</a>.</p>\n<h3>13 choses &agrave; faire avant le changement de th&egrave;me</h3>\n<p><a href="http://wpformation.com/changer-theme-wordpress/">WPFormation propose 13 &eacute;tapes</a> &agrave; ne pas oublier avant un changement de th&egrave;me.</p>\n<h3>Commentaires ou pas commentaires, telle est la question</h3>\n<p>Laissez les commentaires ou pas ? <a href="http://torquemag.io/accept-comments-wordpress-site/">voici ce que vous devez savoir avant de vous d&eacute;cider</a> (en).</p>\n<h3>WPServeur</h3>\n<p>Un <a href="https://www.wpserveur.net/">nouveau service d&rsquo;h&eacute;bergement</a> uniquement pour WordPress&hellip; et en fran&ccedil;ais.</p>\n<h3>Le mus&eacute;e des t-shirt d&rsquo;Automattic</h3>\n<p>Vous ne connaissiez pas le <a href="http://museum.automattic.com/">mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Automattic</a> (en) ? Celui avec les t-shirts des Wordcamps&hellip; et vous verrez m&ecirc;me 2 mod&egrave;les parisiens ! et vous lesquels pr&eacute;f&eacute;rez-vous ?</p>\n<h3>Optimiser sa base de donn&eacute;es</h3>\n<p>Si vous souhaitez optimiser votre base de donn&eacute;es, <a href="http://premium.wpmudev.org/blog/optimizing-your-wordpress-database-a-complete-guide/">lisez cet article de WPMUDEV</a> (en).</p>\n<h3>Daniel Roch a un blog !</h3>\n<p>Ca y est c&rsquo;est officiel, <a href="http://daniel-roch.fr/">Daniel Roch a un blog</a>&hellip; le cr&eacute;ateur de SEOMix a succomb&eacute;&hellip; a force de faire du WordPress compliqu&eacute;, il a d&eacute;cid&eacute; de revenir &agrave; la base : le blog ! &laquo;&nbsp;Mer il es fou !&nbsp;&raquo; <img src="http://www.wordpress-fr.net/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" class="wp-smiley"></p>\n<h3>De la planification de rendez-vous</h3>\n<p>Si vous voulez que vos contacts BuddyPress puisse se fixer des rdv, <a href="http://wpchannel.com/rendez-vous-buddypress-wordpress/">cette extension va vous int&eacute;resser</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=qeRz470Kfzg:mm4RcQf71bY:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=qeRz470Kfzg:mm4RcQf71bY:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=qeRz470Kfzg:mm4RcQf71bY:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=qeRz470Kfzg:mm4RcQf71bY:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=qeRz470Kfzg:mm4RcQf71bY:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=qeRz470Kfzg:mm4RcQf71bY:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></a>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/qeRz470Kfzg" height="1" width="1">\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:74:"BoiteAWeb : WooCommerce Notices Fix : Corrigez votre thème sans y toucher";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:53:"http://boiteaweb.fr/woocommerce-notices-fix-8457.html";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:53:"http://boiteaweb.fr/woocommerce-notices-fix-8457.html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2014-10-20T11:19:26+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"Julio Potier";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:433:"<div>\n<p>WooCommerce Notices Fix est un plugin WordPress gratuit permettant d''emp&ecirc;cher les plugins de cache comme WP Rocket de mettre en cache les notices.</p>\n<p>Cet article <a rel="nofollow" href="http://boiteaweb.fr/woocommerce-notices-fix-8457.html">WooCommerce Notices Fix : Corrigez votre th&egrave;me sans y toucher</a> est apparu en premier sur <a rel="nofollow" href="http://boiteaweb.fr/">BoiteAWeb.fr</a>.</p>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:48:"WP Formation : Passer WordPress de HTTP à HTTPS";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:44:"http://wpformation.com/wordpress-http-https/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:44:"http://wpformation.com/wordpress-http-https/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2014-10-20T08:45:49+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"WPFormation";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1427:"<div>\n<p><img width="300" height="165" src="http://wpformation.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/https-ssl-wordpress1-300x165.jpg" class="attachment-medium wp-post-image" alt="https-ssl-wordpress" style="float: right; margin:0 0 10px 10px;">Dans le cadre du&nbsp;d&eacute;veloppement du site www.WPSERVEUR.net, j&rsquo;ai du passer un site WordPress en version s&eacute;curis&eacute;e, &agrave; savoir de HTTP vers HTTPS. Si cette proc&eacute;dure est relativement simple, elle n&eacute;cessite toutefois quelques &eacute;claircissements et pr&eacute;cautions d&rsquo;usage que je vais m&rsquo;empresser de vous d&eacute;crire dans ce tuto;) D&eacute;finitions SSL &amp;&nbsp;HTTPS Commen&ccedil;ons tout d&rsquo;abord par quelques d&eacute;finitions ...</p>\n<hr>\n<a rel="nofollow" href="http://wpformation.com/wordpress-http-https/">Passer WordPress de HTTP &agrave; HTTPS</a> est un article de <a title="Formation Internet WordPress Ecommerce" href="http://wpformation.com/">WP Formation</a><br><a href="http://wpformation.com/formation-wordpress/">Formation WordPress</a> &amp; <a href="http://wpformation.com/formation-woocommerce-e-commerce/">eCommerce</a> - Retrouvez-moi sur <a title="Ajouter sur Facebook" href="http://www.facebook.com/wpformation">Facebook</a> - <a title="Suivre sur Twitter" href="http://twitter.com/wpformation">Twitter</a> - <a href="http://plus.google.com/+FabriceDucarme/">Google+</a><br><hr>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:52:"WordPress Channel : Des dispos pour un rendez-vous ?";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:54:"http://wpchannel.com/rendez-vous-buddypress-wordpress/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:54:"http://wpchannel.com/rendez-vous-buddypress-wordpress/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2014-10-17T19:30:04+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"Mathieu Viet";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:765:"<div>\n<p>Il y a quelque temps, je vous faisais (re)d&eacute;couvrir BuddyPress, le plugin WordPress qui dynamise votre communaut&eacute;. Nous avons notamment vu qu&rsquo;il &eacute;tait organis&eacute; en composants autonomes activables selon vos besoins et que son utilisation de la WordPress plugin API et ses nombreuses fonctions et API communautaires ouvraient un champ des possibles extraordinaire en mati&egrave;re&hellip;</p>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" href="http://wpchannel.com/author/imath/">Mathieu Viet</a> - <a rel="nofollow" href="http://wpchannel.com/">WordPress Channel - Tutoriels, th&egrave;mes &amp; plugins WordPress</a> - <a rel="nofollow" href="http://wpchannel.com/rendez-vous-buddypress-wordpress/">Des dispos pour un rendez-vous ?</a></p>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:41:"GD6D : Twenty Fifteen : simple et elegant";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/Gd6d/~3/uAorU5Z8zJ4/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:51:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/Gd6d/~3/uAorU5Z8zJ4/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2014-10-16T12:10:33+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Gd6d";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7067:"<div>\n<img src="http://i1.wp.com/www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Am_I_Responsive_.jpg?fit=1024%2C1024" class="attachment-large wp-post-image" alt="Am_I_Responsive_"><h2>Le prochain th&egrave;me par d&eacute;faut Twenty Fifteen&nbsp;est magnifique, ax&eacute; sur la simplicit&eacute; et la lisibilit&eacute;</h2>\n<p>Avec un choix pertinent de typographie (Noto Serif et Sans de Google), ce th&egrave;me valorise le contenu et&nbsp;le texte comme une partie importante de l&rsquo;interface utilisateur.<br>\nLa navigation verticale et statique est en rupture avec les th&egrave;mes pr&eacute;c&eacute;dents et la tendance actuelle. Mais c&rsquo;est bien de changer, personnellement j&rsquo;aime bien !<br>\nA noter que la barre verticale avec le menu reste statique, comme au bon vieux temps des iframes !</p>\n<p>Le th&egrave;me est &eacute;galement con&ccedil;u pour maximiser l&rsquo;impact des outils de personnalisation de base : en-t&ecirc;tes personnalis&eacute;s et Fond de page. En quelques clics, votre site sera unique. L&rsquo;image &agrave; la une des articles et pages est aussi valoris&eacute;e car bien visible en haut de bloc principal, sans marge.</p>\n<p>Dernier point, mais non des moindres, Twenty Fifteen utilise une approche &laquo;&nbsp;Mobile&nbsp;&raquo; dans sa conception. Le th&egrave;me reste attractif sur tous les supports. L&rsquo;exp&eacute;rience de navigation est partout optimale !</p>\n<p>Twenty Fifteen est donc un th&egrave;me par d&eacute;faut simple, facile &agrave; prendre en main par les d&eacute;butants pour s&rsquo;initier &agrave; WordPress et pourquoi pas comme base pour un site plus complexe. Je ne serais d&rsquo;ailleurs pas surpris de trouver bient&ocirc;t de nombreux th&egrave;me enfant pour y apporter des fonctions suppl&eacute;mentaires.</p>\n<p>Sources :<br>\nTraduction libre de <a href="https://make.wordpress.org/core/2014/09/09/twenty-fifteen/">https://make.wordpress.org/core/2014/09/09/twenty-fifteen/<br></a><a href="http://wptavern.com/first-look-at-designs-for-the-twenty-fifteen-default-wordpress-theme">http://wptavern.com/first-look-at-designs-for-the-twenty-fifteen-default-wordpress-theme</a></p>\n<h2>Utilisation</h2>\n<p>Personnellement, j&rsquo;aime beaucoup ce th&egrave;me et j&rsquo;ai d&eacute;cid&eacute; de l&rsquo;installer pour site <a href="http://www.wp-formation.com/">http://www.wp-formation.com/</a><br>\nPremi&egrave;re constat, il fonctionne bien, est tr&egrave;s facile d&rsquo;utilisation, et ce avec tr&egrave;s peu de r&eacute;glages. Ils sont tous regroup&eacute;s dans le mode &laquo;&nbsp;Personnaliser&nbsp;&raquo; : il n&rsquo;y a ensuite ni mod&egrave;le de page, ni codes particuliers. A vous d&rsquo;installer <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/shortcodes-ultimate/">une extension de shortcodes</a> pour avoir&nbsp; plus de possibilit&eacute;s.</p>\n<p><a title="Voir le site " href="http://www.wp-formation.com/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3506" src="http://i2.wp.com/www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/twenty-fifteen-wordpress.jpg?resize=500%2C234" alt="twenty-fifteen-wordpress" data-recalc-dims="1"></a></p>\n<div class="shortcode-toggle toggle-telecharger-la-version-beta closed default border">\n<h4 class="toggle-trigger"><a href="http://www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr#">T&eacute;l&eacute;charger la version b&eacute;ta</a></h4>\n<div class="toggle-content">\n<a href="https://make.wordpress.org/core/2014/10/14/twenty-fifteen-is-here/">https://make.wordpress.org/core/2014/10/14/twenty-fifteen-is-here/<br></a>Le th&egrave;me est encore en version b&eacute;ta, mais je n&rsquo;ai pas trouv&eacute; de bug&hellip; </div>\n<!--/.toggle-content-->\n<input type="hidden" name="title_open" value="Fermer "><input type="hidden" name="title_closed" value="T&eacute;l&eacute;charger la version b&eacute;ta">\n</div>\n<!--/.shortcode-toggle-->\n<div class="shortcode-toggle toggle-personnaliser-limage-den-tete closed default border">\n<h4 class="toggle-trigger"><a href="http://www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr#">Personnaliser l''image d''en-t&ecirc;te</a></h4>\n<div class="toggle-content">L&rsquo;image d&rsquo;en-t&ecirc;te est en r&eacute;alit&eacute; le fond de la colonne. La taille de l&rsquo;image est atypique : 954 x 13000, pour un affichage sur grand &eacute;cran<br><a href="http://i0.wp.com/www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Personnaliser-image-entete.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3498" src="http://i0.wp.com/www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Personnaliser-image-entete-300x196.jpg?resize=300%2C196" alt="Personnaliser-image-entete" data-recalc-dims="1"></a> </div>\n<!--/.toggle-content-->\n<input type="hidden" name="title_open" value="Fermer "><input type="hidden" name="title_closed" value="Personnaliser l''image d''en-t&ecirc;te">\n</div>\n<!--/.shortcode-toggle-->\n<div class="shortcode-toggle toggle-personnaliser-les-couleurs closed default border">\n<h4 class="toggle-trigger"><a href="http://www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr#">Personnaliser les couleurs</a></h4>\n<div class="toggle-content">Le th&egrave;me propose 6 ambiances couleurs diff&eacute;rentes, et 4 menus d&nbsp;&raquo;roulants pour d&eacute;finir avec pr&eacute;cisions les couleurs du menu, du texte et d&rsquo;arri&egrave;re plan colonne et fond de page<br><a href="http://i0.wp.com/www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/personnaliser-couleurs.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3497" src="http://i0.wp.com/www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/personnaliser-couleurs.jpg?resize=300%2C196" alt="personnaliser-couleurs" data-recalc-dims="1"></a>\n</div>\n<!--/.toggle-content-->\n<input type="hidden" name="title_open" value="Fermer "><input type="hidden" name="title_closed" value="Personnaliser les couleurs">\n</div>\n<!--/.shortcode-toggle-->\n<div class="shortcode-toggle toggle-gerer-les-menus closed default border">\n<h4 class="toggle-trigger"><a href="http://www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr#">G&eacute;rer les menus</a></h4>\n<div class="toggle-content">Le th&egrave;me propose 2 menus : la barre de navigation avec sous menu (et zone de clic pratique pour la prise en main tactile) et un menu social. Ce menu fonctionne avec les liens du menu : gr&acirc;ce au code CSS, une image s&rsquo;affiche en fonction de la destination du lien. L&rsquo;intitul&eacute; est donc facultatif.\n<p><a href="http://i2.wp.com/www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Menus_%E2%80%B9_Formation_WordPress_%E2%80%94_WordPress.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3501" src="http://i2.wp.com/www.gd6d.fr/wordpressfr/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Menus_%E2%80%B9_Formation_WordPress_%E2%80%94_WordPress.jpg?resize=300%2C176" alt="Menus_&lsaquo;_Formation_WordPress_&mdash;_WordPress" data-recalc-dims="1"></a></p>\n</div>\n<!--/.toggle-content-->\n<input type="hidden" name="title_open" value="Fermer "><input type="hidden" name="title_closed" value="G&eacute;rer les menus">\n</div>\n<!--/.shortcode-toggle-->\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Gd6d/~4/uAorU5Z8zJ4" height="1" width="1">\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:41:"L''écho des plugins WordPress : GD MyList";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:53:"http://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/gd-mylist/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:53:"http://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/gd-mylist/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2014-10-15T09:41:45+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"Li-An";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:39:"<div>Des favoris pour vos membres</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"Grégoire Noyelle : WordPress :: Very French Trip Podcast #6";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://www.gregoirenoyelle.com/wordpress-very-french-trip-podcast-6/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:68:"http://www.gregoirenoyelle.com/wordpress-very-french-trip-podcast-6/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2014-10-14T06:25:44+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17:"Grégoire Noyelle";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:743:"<div>Sixi&egrave;me &eacute;dition du Podcast WordPress Very French Trip Aujourd&rsquo;hui nous accueillons Alex Bortolotti Jonathan Buttigieg&nbsp;qui sont venu nous parler de th&egrave;me et de plugins premiums. Je cite imath qui nous a concocter le post cette semaine: Alex est notamment le cr&eacute;ateur du th&egrave;me &laquo; &eacute;tendard &raquo; que vous p