it&eacute;s J&eacute;r&eacute;my Herv&eacute; et Alex Concha, tous deux automatticiens, autrement dit, employ&eacute; de la soci&eacute;t&eacute; Automattic, cr&eacute;&eacute;e par Matt Mullenweg. Je cite l&rsquo;article: Nous avons parl&eacute; de l&rsquo;organisation particuli&egrave;re de cette soci&eacute;t&eacute; o&ugrave; tout le monde intervient &agrave; distance. Du coup, pas mal de [&hellip;]<p>Cet article a &eacute;t&eacute; publi&eacute; le 25 octobre 2014 par <a href="http://www.gregoirenoyelle.com/">Gr&eacute;goire Noyelle</a>. Pour le lire en ligne, suivre le lien: <a href="http://www.gregoirenoyelle.com/wordpress-very-french-trip-podcast-7/">WordPress :: Very French Trip Podcast #7</a>.</p>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"WP Formation : Divi 2 Thème hybride pour WordPress";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:46:"http://wpformation.com/divi-2-theme-wordpress/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:46:"http://wpformation.com/divi-2-theme-wordpress/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2014-10-25T09:05:11+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"WPFormation";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1355:"<div>\n<p><img width="300" height="130" src="http://wpformation.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/divi-2-modules1-300x130.jpg" class="attachment-medium wp-post-image" alt="divi-2-modules" style="float: right; margin:0 0 10px 10px;">Je connaissais&nbsp;les Frameworks, les th&egrave;mes premium aux nombreuses&nbsp;options et les plugins &laquo;&nbsp;constructeur de pages&nbsp;&raquo;,&nbsp;en revanche,&nbsp;je ne connaissais pas DIVI 2,&nbsp;le petit dernier de chez Elegant Themes. Force est de constater que c&rsquo;&eacute;tait une erreur que je vais m&rsquo;empresser de corriger avec cet article;) Framework ou&nbsp;Constructeur de pages ? On sait que de plus en plus ...</p>\n<hr>\n<a rel="nofollow" href="http://wpformation.com/divi-2-theme-wordpress/">Divi 2 Th&egrave;me hybride pour WordPress</a> est un article de <a title="Formation Internet WordPress Ecommerce" href="http://wpformation.com/">WP Formation</a><br><a href="http://wpformation.com/formation-wordpress/">Formation WordPress</a> &amp; <a href="http://wpformation.com/formation-woocommerce-e-commerce/">eCommerce</a> - Retrouvez-moi sur <a title="Ajouter sur Facebook" href="http://www.facebook.com/wpformation">Facebook</a> - <a title="Suivre sur Twitter" href="http://twitter.com/wpformation">Twitter</a> - <a href="http://plus.google.com/+FabriceDucarme/">Google+</a><br><hr>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8